Please refer to the COPYING file for a copy of the license.


Installation
============
Please refer to the INSTALL file for instructions on installation.


Usage
=====
Before using Website Baker please note: you must not remove/change
the license footer of the Administration. Also, it is much
appreciated if you leave a link somewhere on your website, which
links to the Website Baker website. (http://www.websitebaker.org/) 


F.A.Q. and Help/Documentation
=============================
Please refer to the official Website Documentation website:
http://www.websitebaker.org/docs
Also, you may wish to visit the Website Baker official forum website:
http://www.websitebaker.org/forum


Bug Reports
===========
Please visit our project bug tracker at:
http://www.websitebaker.org/bugs
Don't forget to state ALL details, including WB version.

Donations
=========
If you would like to make a donation please visit:
http://www.websitebaker.org/ for more information.

